jminusminus

Enum TokenKind

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<TokenKind>
      • jminusminus.TokenKind
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<TokenKind>

     enum TokenKind
extends Enum<TokenKind>
    An enum of token kinds. Each entry in this enum represents the kind of a token along with its image (string representation).

    When you add a new token to the scanner, you must also add an entry to this enum specifying the kind and image of the new token.
